{
  "text": "Where, n = x or y The impedance of the resonant networks Z= 8.16 \u2126 (Ly, Cy) and Z=4.85\u2126 (Lx,Cx). The values of impedance of these dual auxiliary resonant networks always less than the output voltage versus maximum input current ratio [CITATION_1] , then the soft-switching condition can be obtained for all switching devices of the converter.",
